{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dice with the Devil: Rerolled is a deckbuilder autobattler about scoring the best out of three dice rolls.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Win souls from your opponents and design your hand of three dice to out-luck your opponents and advance through the areas of the casino.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972600/extras/endless_runs.png?t=1738346459\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>NOT A ROGUELIKE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Losing battles only loses the souls you wager, so don't be afraid to experiment and try new strategies! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972600/extras/unlock_new_dice.png?t=1738346459\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972600/extras/dicetionarygif.gif?t=1738346459\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Complete fun challenges to unlock new dice</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From drawing with your opponent, to rolling over 100 with three dice, overcoming them is key to success! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972600/extras/build_your_hand.png?t=1738346459\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972600/extras/inventorygif5.gif?t=1738346459\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Buy dice for your hand and customise them with stickers</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stickers add new abilities to dice that enhance your roll and help you win.<br>With thousands of possible combinations, you control if luck will be on your side. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972600/extras/steal_their_souls.png?t=1738346459\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972600/extras/battlegif2.gif?t=1738346459\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Battle unique opponents in different arenas</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The further you progress, the more advanced their strategies become. Synergies and counters are key to beating them all. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972600/extras/dice.png?t=1738346459\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972600/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738346459","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972600/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738346459","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972600/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738346459","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972600/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738346459","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3437840,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dice with the Devil: Rerolled is a deckbuilder autobattler about scoring the best out of three dice rolls.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Win souls from your opponents and design your hand of three dice to out-luck your opponents and advance through the areas of the casino.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972600/extras/endless_runs.png?t=1738346459\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>NOT A ROGUELIKE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Losing battles only loses the souls you wager